# graphify — generated knowledge graph output.
# Tracked: graph.json (queryable graph) + GRAPH_REPORT.md.
# Ignored: cache/, graph.html, manifest.json, cost.json — all rebuildable.
# NB: must be `graphify-out/*`, not `graphify-out/` — git will not descend
# into an excluded directory, so the negations below would never apply.
graphify-out/*
!graphify-out/graph.json
!graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md
